data.description: Charming farmhouse with private setting.  Home features beautiful dining room with build-in shelves, nice living room and main floor full bath.  Fresh paint throughout!  Large rear deck with lots of privacy and detached 2 car garage.  Chicken coop stays and is ready for your flock!   This property offers a convenient location and a park-like setting with fruit trees, blueberries, grapes and even Passion Fruit flowers.
